        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer331207108" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13627872122108597536">Well, it&apos;d be foolish for me to review my own book... I poured my heart and soul into ROOTLESS, and spent a very happy twelve months working on the novel. To say the story is an important part of my life would be a huge understatement, and I gave it my all. So thanks to those who take the time to read my debut novel and share their thoughts on it. Though I should warn people who&apos;ve yet to read it - watch out for spoilers! :)<br/>CHEERS,<br/>Chris<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText13627872122108597536" style="display:none">Well, it'd be foolish for me to review my own book... I poured my heart and soul into ROOTLESS, and spent a very happy twelve months working on the novel. To say the story is an important part of my life would be a huge understatement, and I gave it my all. So thanks to those who take the time to read my debut novel and share their thoughts on it. Though I should warn people who've yet to read it - watch out for spoilers! :)<br />CHEERS,<br />Chris<br /></span>
