<span id="freeTextContainer11070598940622710117">I&apos;m the author of <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13591672-rootless/' rel='nofollow noopener'>ROOTLESS</a> (Scholastic), as well as the follow-up <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21881461-the-rift' rel='nofollow noopener'>THE RIFT</a>, and the final book of this &quot;Mad Max meets Lord of the Rings&quot; tree-logy, <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/24760233-the-reckoning' rel='nofollow noopener'>THE RECKONING</a>... Also the author of the rad new sci-fi thriller <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25550544-night-speed' rel='nofollow noopener'>NIGHT SPEED</a>. I live in Denver, but grew up not far from London. I studied natural resources in college, then spent eight years leading wilderness adventure trips for high school students. </span>
  <span id="freeText11070598940622710117" style="display:none">I'm the author of <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13591672-rootless/" rel="nofollow noopener">ROOTLESS</a> (Scholastic), as well as the follow-up <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/21881461-the-rift" rel="nofollow noopener">THE RIFT</a>, and the final book of this "Mad Max meets Lord of the Rings" tree-logy, <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/24760233-the-reckoning" rel="nofollow noopener">THE RECKONING</a>... Also the author of the rad new sci-fi thriller <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/25550544-night-speed" rel="nofollow noopener">NIGHT SPEED</a>. I live in Denver, but grew up not far from London. I studied natural resources in college, then spent eight years leading wilderness adventure trips for high school students. I like to write more than anything else I've ever done, though reading is right up there, too.<br /><a href="http://www.facebook.com/ChrisHowardBooks" rel="nofollow noopener">Join me on Facebook</a><br /><a href="https://www.instagram.com/chrish0ward/" rel="nofollow noopener">Join me on Instagram</a><br /><a href="http://chrishowardbooks.tumblr.com/" rel="nofollow noopener">Join me on Tumblr</a><br /><a href="http://twitter.com/chrisH0WARD" rel="nofollow noopener">Join me on Twitter</a></span>
